OL,3,CSigns of confusion: Moves to end
OL,4,Cperplexing parking signs
OL,6,FNew figures show 81% of motorists find
OL,7,Fparking signs confusing, as ITV News'
OL,8,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,10,FNew figures have revealed many
OL,11,Fmotorists are confused by parking
OL,12,Fsigns - often ending up with drivers
OL,13,Ffacing fines.
OL,15,FData given to ITV News shows 81% of
OL,16,Fdrivers believe parking signs are
OL,17,Fconfusing - with 30% of motorists who
OL,18,Fappeal fines citing signage as a
OL,19,Fproblem.
