OL,3,CSigns of confusion: Moves to end
OL,4,Cperplexing parking signs
OL,6,FThe new figures were compiled for
OL,7,FConfused.com through research
OL,8,Finvolving thousands of motorists.
OL,10,FIn Surrey, we spoke to a plumber,
OL,11,FPerry Rand, who parked his van at a
OL,12,Flocal supermarket for around five
OL,13,Fminutes - and got a #100 fine.
OL,15,FThe parking sign said "no commercial
OL,16,Fvehicles", but it had bits of the
OL,17,Fwording missing.
