OL,6,FHe told ITV News: "I've never heard of
OL,7,Fgoing to the shop and not being able
OL,8,Fto park a van. You can see that they
OL,9,Fput a sticker over a previous point on
OL,10,Fthe sign."
OL,12,FThe parking sector has just
OL,13,Fimplemented a new code setting fresh
OL,14,Fstandards for signs.
OL,16,FITV News spoke to one of the sectors'
OL,17,Fleading spokesman, Will Hurley of the
OL,18,FInternational Parking Community.
