OL,3,CSigns of confusion: Moves to end
OL,4,Cperplexing parking signs
OL,6,FHe said: "There is no benefit to
OL,7,Fmisleading signs. Ultimately, as an
OL,8,Findustry we want to make parking
OL,9,Fforgettable... you must meet a certain
OL,10,Fcriteria which deals with their
OL,11,Fcontent, how clear they are."
OL,13,FThe new rules affect all new signs and
OL,14,Fmandate changes to existing ones.
OL,16,FAround a fifth of parking fines are
OL,17,Fdished out around Christmas, and, for
OL,18,Fmany who get one, unclear signage is a
OL,19,Fproblem that has itself been parked
OL,20,Ffar too long.
