OL,6,FWhat advice is there for drivers who
OL,7,Fare confused by parking signs?
OL,9,FThe British Parking Association (BPA),
OL,10,Fwhich represents the UK's parking
OL,11,Fsector, told ITV News that drivers
OL,12,Ffaced with confusing parking signs
OL,13,Fshould find answers to these questions:
OL,15,FWhat can people do if they come across
OL,16,Fa confusing sign?
OL,18,FThe BPA said they welcome any feedback
OL,19,Fand suggestions on signs.
