OL,6,FFor specific signage concerns, they
OL,7,Fsaid motorists should write to the BPA
OL,8,Fand share examples of signs that
OL,9,Fbreach the Single Code of Practice
OL,10,Frequirements, or where suggestions for
OL,11,Fimprovements can be made.
OL,13,FWhat is being done to make signs clear?
OL,15,FThe Single Sector Code of Practice has
OL,16,Fbeen in place since the start October,
OL,17,Fand places a number of new
OL,18,Frequirements on private parking
OL,19,Foperators with regard to their signs.
