OL,4,Cperplexing parking signs
OL,6,FThe new Code tightens the obligations
OL,7,Fon private parking operators, ensuring
OL,8,Fsigns at the entrance and within the
OL,9,Fcarpark are clearly visible and have
OL,10,Fall the information drivers need.
OL,12,FSigns must also include information
OL,13,Fabout the parking operator, tariff and
OL,14,Fcharge that may apply if drivers
OL,15,Fbreach the terms and conditions.
OL,17,FFor advice on parking signs near you,
OL,18,Fplease visit the parking sign
OL,19,Ftranslator.
